<topic id="topic6">
   <title>pgAdmin 4 for Greenplum Database</title>
   <body>
      <draft-comment author="msk">pgAdmin 4 </draft-comment>
      <p>If you prefer a graphic interface, use pgAdmin 4 for Greenplum Database. This GUI client
         supports PostgreSQL databases with all standard pgAdmin 4 features, while adding support
         for Greenplum-specific features. </p>
      <p>pgAdmin 4 for Greenplum Database supports the following Greenplum-specific features:</p>
      <ul>
         <li id="io147510">External tables</li>
         <li id="io147522">Append-optimized tables, including compressed append-optimized
            tables</li>
         <li id="io147523">Table partitioning</li>
         <li id="io147524">Resource queues</li>
         <li id="io147525">Graphical <codeph>EXPLAIN ANALYZE</codeph>
         </li>
      </ul>
